{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The shoulders, and I also had the pleurisy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what I was treated for in the Jew-- Jewish hospital in Trastevere in Rome for a long period of time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then afterwards, it was very lovely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sent me to a villa nearby Rome, which was what they call a sanatorium, which is to recover.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there I was recuperating there for probably many months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have no recollection how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess gradually.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was more or less in Italy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just couldn't eat enough of that beautiful fruit, which I have seen the first time in many a years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it started, I suppose, in Italy where I knew that things will get better from now on and when I realized that finally the war is over, and, of course, the sadness that-- I don't know whether I'd given up already hope then, I don't know, but I do know that I didn't think there is much hope that I find my parents ever, that they must have perished.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess it never will.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My [INAUDIBLE] I still feel that she's somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About a year and a half, and I stayed with the family Levine all this time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by now I am-- let's see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born in '28. 20-- well, I guess--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "18, 19 By then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The English.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fortunately my father saw to it that we studied languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while my sister spoke a beautiful English, and, in fact, I remember she was getting book of the month club books in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My English, whatever I knew, was at least grammatically correct, and I managed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then it has greatly improved in Montreal, and I spoke English only.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Especially the family Levine.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
